        <initializer>127</initializer>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Represents the PHY constant aMaxPhyPacketSize, see section 11.3. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>Currently only 127 byte sized packets are supported although some PHYs (e.g. SUN, MSK, LECIM, ...) support larger packet sizes. Needs to be changed once those PHYs should be fully supported. </para>
