      <memberdef kind="define" id="group__ieee802154__l2_1ga1243000b59167777e078060fd3c1c218" prot="public" static="no">
        <name>IEEE802154_FCS_LENGTH</name>
        <initializer>2</initializer>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Represents the frame check sequence length, see section 7.2.1.1. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>Currently only a 2 byte FCS is supported although some PHYs (e.g. SUN, TVWS, ...) optionally support a 4 byte FCS. Needs to be changed once those PHYs should be fully supported. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
